Tanvir Gill Origin/Culture/Country: Indian

Tanvir Gill: was an anchor on the Indian business news channel CNBC-TV18.She completed her graduation from Jesus & Mary College, Delhi University and her MBA from Lal Bahadur Shastri Institute of Management[1], Delhi. She worked with the TV Today Network before joining TV18 Network. She is an NCFM-NSE certified mutual fund advisor. While at CNBC-TV18, she hosted morning band shows like Your Stocks and Mid Cap Radar. She also anchored the hugely popular segment, "Saas Bahu & Sensex", along with Ayesha Faridi[1] and provided reports for the CNBC Asia programs CNBC's Cash Flow and Capital Connection.
